Hi,

Thanks for your time. And I will say it again. ABP is GREAT, Some questions:

Why do I need to make the following method virtual to make UOW work?

``` c#
public virtual GetLocationMappingsOutput GetLocationMappings(GetLocationMappingsInput aInput)
```

Here is the relevant controller code:

``` c#
